org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.writers.def
Interface IAeWriterDefVisitorFactory

public interface IAeWriterDefVisitorFactory

A factory interface for creating writer def visitors. The dispatch writer uses this to create a writer def visitor to dispatch to.
